high_descs: Move to the small round table in the corner.
Pick up the candle from the table.
Bring the candle to the dining table.
Put the candle on the black plate in the middle.
Pick up that plate from the table.
Bring the plate to the TV stand.
Put the plate on the TV stand.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a candle on it on the TV stand.

high_descs: Cross the room to the far wall, then turn left and continue along the wall to a low table in the next corner.
Get the candle that is on the table.
Turn around and go behind the brown sofa, turning right to go between the table and two brown chairs, then turn left and go to the table, between the two dining chairs.
Place the candle on the left front corner of the plate closest to you.
Pick up the plate with the candle on it.
Turn around and go to the left of the pair of brown chairs, past the fireplace to the stand holding the TV screen.
Put the plate on the end of the stand closest to the fireplace, with the candle in the nearest right corner.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate holding a candle on a TV stand.

high_descs: Walk to the chair in front of you then turn left and walk all the way to the circular end table that's in front of you.
Pick up the small object on the circular table in front of you.
Turn around and walk until the rug underfoot ends then turn right and walk until you are lined up with the center of the table to your left then turn and walk to the table and face it.
Put the item on the plate to the right of the credit card.
Pick up the plate with the object on it.
Walk over to the tv on the left side of the tv so you are facing the length of the tv in front of you.
Place the plate on the tv stand in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a strange object on it on the tv stand.
